      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONCE A DREAM (6) has mixed form but was in the money three back and wasn't far away last time at this track when fifth (19.64) in a Grade 4. Has the ability and expected to go close. BLACK HOAX (7) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten a neck, (19.63) at this track. Must be included in calculations. PINAROO FLYER (3) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when third (19.57) at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to feature again. CABAO KYANITE (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
